This addendum extends the JusticeFlow Case Management API (v2.1.0) to include Caseflow Efficiency Metrics. These metrics aggregate case resolution data to generate efficiency scores for courtrooms and assigned counsel. The data is exposed via dedicated analytics endpoints to support supervisor dashboards used for staffing and backlog reduction planning.

